snippet.title: Prologue Demo Trailer | Power Sink
snippet.description:
Thank you to the lovely people organising the ANZ Indie Showcase!
We're thrilled to be able to take part and are super excited to show people what Power Sink has to offer 🥳

Check out the brand new demo on Steam today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2289740/Power_Sink/

Follow us on our Socials:
https://linktr.ee/winterwiregames

Join us on our Discord:
https://discord.gg/93DzHw2Sad

For our Press kits, check out our website:
https://winterwiregames.com/

Thank you to Screenwest for supporting us in making Power Sink!
